</dl>
<p><b>Sode</b><sup id="cite_ref-Dalby_4-13" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Dalby-4" title=""><span>[</span>5<span>]</span></a></sup> 袖</p>
<dl>
<dd>sleeve</dd>
</dl>
<p><b>Sodeguchi</b> 袖口</p>
